251
00:12:59,947 --> 00:13:01,347
Apa?

252
00:13:01,347 --> 00:13:02,647
Salah!

253
00:13:02,647 --> 00:13:06,047
Itu adalah Mumi yang telah kau pasangkan topengmu!

254
00:13:06,047 --> 00:13:09,347
Seperti yang Shinichi deduksikan!

255
00:13:12,047 --> 00:13:14,847
Berhentilah bertingkah berandal!

256
00:13:14,847 --> 00:13:17,647
Aku satu-satunya Manusia Serigala di sini!

257
00:13:17,647 --> 00:13:20,447
Dan Manusia Serigala!

258
00:13:20,447 --> 00:13:23,347
Apa kau sungguh meminum koktail itu?

259
00:13:23,347 --> 00:13:25,747
