261
00:13:28,447 --> 00:13:30,947
Yah. Untuk menyegarkanku.

262
00:13:30,947 --> 00:13:32,747
Atau, apa maksudmu

263
00:13:32,747 --> 00:13:35,647
Manusia Serigala seharusnya tidak minum minuman keras?

264
00:13:37,247 --> 00:13:39,647
Kau sungguh meminum Silver Bullet?

265
00:13:39,647 --> 00:13:40,947
Diam, berandal!

266
00:13:40,947 --> 00:13:42,847
Aku meminumnya!

267
00:13:42,847 --> 00:13:44,547
Silver Bullet?

268
00:13:46,747 --> 00:13:48,147
Hei, tidak mungkin.

269
00:13:48,147 --> 00:13:49,647
Silver Bullet?

270
