498
00:29:06,753 --> 00:29:09,453
Jika dia tidak datang,

499
00:29:09,453 --> 00:29:12,553
Keadaan tidak akan jadi seperti ini.

500
00:29:12,553 --> 00:29:15,053
Jadi...

501
00:29:15,053 --> 00:29:18,053
Tangkap orang yang bernama Vermouth juga!

502
00:29:18,053 --> 00:29:19,153
Dan?

503
00:29:19,153 --> 00:29:21,453
